clusters   generate 3D views of some predefined cluster shapes using RGL rendering
dimer_linear   extinction spectrum of a dimer of gold nanorods
dimer_cd   circular dichroism for a chiral dimer of gold nanorods
helix_cd   circular dichroism for a helix of gold nanoparticles
dispersion     spectra for multiple angles of incidence
averaging     compare the angle-averaged spectrum with spectra at fixed orientations
lattice_sum     lattice sum for a 2D square array of dipoles
diffractive   extinction spectrum of a linear chain and array of gold nanorods
shell   absorption spectrum of a spherical shell of dye molecules
dimer_dye   absorption spectrum of a dimer of dyes
low_level   exposing low-level steps in the calculations
method   testing order-of-scattering and conjugate gradient methods to solve the coupled-dipole equations
quadrature   testing the accuracy of different quadrature methods
